they
were
rattling
upon
their
journey.
"Is
it
far?"
asked
Douglas
Stone.
"Oh,
no.
We
have
a
very
little
quiet
place
off
the
Euston
Road."
The
surgeon
pressed
the
spring
of
his
repeater
and
listened
to
the
little
